    <div class="container">
        <h1>Unlock Your Potential with AI-Powered Learning</h1>
        <p>Personalized study plans, instant doubt clarification, and adaptive mock tests designed for JEE & NEET aspirants.</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started Now</a>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="features">
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Why Choose PrepAI?</h2>
        <p class="section-intro">We provide cutting-edge tools to make your exam preparation smarter, not just harder.</p>
        <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-brain"></i></div>
                <h3>Adaptive Learning</h3>
                <p>Our AI adjusts the difficulty and content based on your performance, ensuring you master every concept.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-comments"></i></div>
                <h3>Instant Doubt Solving</h3>
                <p>Get your questions answered 24/7 by our AI tutor, trained on a vast knowledge base of exam topics.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line"></i></div>
                <h3>Performance Analytics</h3>
                <p>Track your progress with detailed reports, identify your weak areas, and receive actionable insights.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="bg-[#F8F9FA] py-20 md:py-32 text-center">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-[#0B2A4F] leading-tight">
            Supercharge Your Exam Prep with AI
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg md:text-xl text-[#6C757D] max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            From instant doubt solving to infinite practice questions, PrepAI is your personal AI tutor for JEE, NEET, and MHT-CET success.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8">
            <a href="#features" class="bg-[#00C49A] text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg hover:bg-teal-600 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg text-lg">
                Explore Features
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Features Section -->
<section id="features" class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
             <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#0B2A4F]">Your All-in-One AI Study Toolkit</h2>
             <p class="text-[#6C757D] mt-2">Everything you need to study smarter, not just harder.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
            <!-- Feature 1: Snap & Solve -->
            <a href="/doubt" class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-camera-retro text-3xl text-[#00C49A] mb-4"></i>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#0B2A4F] mb-2">Snap & Solve</h3>
                <p class="text-[#6C757D]">Upload a picture of any question and get instant, step-by-step solutions.</p>
            </a>
            <!-- Feature 2: Question Generator -->
            <a href="/generator" class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-infinity text-3xl text-[#00C49A] mb-4"></i>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#0B2A4F] mb-2">Question Generator</h3>
                <p class="text-[#6C757D]">Generate limitless, exam-style questions for any topic and difficulty.</p>
            </a>
            <!-- Feature 3: Revision Tool -->
            <a href="/revision" class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-brain text-3xl text-[#00C49A] mb-4"></i>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#0B2A4F] mb-2">Revision Tool</h3>
                <p class="text-[#6C757D]">Create mnemonics, flashcards, and summaries from your notes instantly.</p>
            </a>
            <!-- Feature 4: Mock Test -->
            <a href="/test" class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-file-pen text-3xl text-[#00C49A] mb-4"></i>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#0B2A4F] mb-2">AI Mock Tests</h3>
                <p class="text-[#6C757D]">Take personalized tests and get detailed performance feedback from AI.</p>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Study Materials Section -->
<section class="bg-white py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
             <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#0B2A4F]">Study Materials (Free)</h2>
             <p class="text-[#6C757D] mt-2">A curated list of high-quality, free resources to boost your exam preparation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <!-- Card 1: JEE Main PYP -->
            <div class="bg-[#F8F9FA] p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200 flex flex-col hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-file-lines text-3xl text-[#00C49A] mb-4"></i>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#0B2A4F] mb-2">JEE Main Previous Papers</h3>
                <p class="text-[#6C757D] flex-grow mb-4">Download official previous year question papers with complete solutions.</p>
                <a href="#" class="font-semibold text-[#00C49A] hover:text-teal-600 transition-colors">Download <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right ml-1"></i></a>
            </div>
            <!-- Card 2: JEE Advanced PYP -->
            <div class="bg-[#F8F9FA] p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200 flex flex-col hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-file-zipper text-3xl text-[#00C49A] mb-4"></i>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#0B2A4F] mb-2">JEE Advanced Previous Papers</h3>
                <p class="text-[#6C757D] flex-grow mb-4">Access a collection of papers to master the toughest questions.</p>
                <a href="#" class="font-semibold text-[#00C49A] hover:text-teal-600 transition-colors">Download <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right ml-1"></i></a>
            </div>
            <!-- Card 3: NEET Resources -->
            <div class="bg-[#F8F9FA] p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200 flex flex-col hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-book-medical text-3xl text-[#00C49A] mb-4"></i>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#0B2A4F] mb-2">NEET Study Materials</h3>
                <p class="text-[#6C757D] flex-grow mb-4">Find chapter-wise notes, practice sheets, and mock tests for NEET.</p>
                <a href="#" class="font-semibold text-[#00C49A] hover:text-teal-600 transition-colors">Explore <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right ml-1"></i></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


<!-- FAQ Section -->
<section class="bg-[#F8F9FA] py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center text-[#0B2A4F] mb-10">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-4" id="faq-container">
            <!-- Question 1 -->
            <div class="faq-item bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300">
                <button class="faq-question w-full flex justify-between items-center text-left p-5 hover:bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
                    <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#0B2A4F]">What kind of problems can I solve with the "Snap & Solve" feature?</span>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down transition-transform duration-300"></i>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer hidden p-5 border-t border-gray-200">
                    <p class="text-[#6C757D]">You can upload images of almost any printed or handwritten question, especially those from subjects like Physics, Chemistry, and Mathematics that may include complex diagrams, formulas, or equations. Our AI is designed to interpret both the text and the visual elements to provide a comprehensive solution.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Question 2 -->
            <div class="faq-item bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300">
                <button class="faq-question w-full flex justify-between items-center text-left p-5 hover:bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
                    <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#0B2A4F]">Are the questions from the "Infinite Question Generator" original?</span>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down transition-transform duration-300"></i>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer hidden p-5 border-t border-gray-200">
                    <p class="text-[#6C757D]">Yes, absolutely. The AI generates brand-new, unseen questions on demand based on the topic and difficulty you select. While they are designed to mimic the style and format of real exams like JEE and NEET, they are not just copies of previous year questions. This provides a limitless supply of fresh practice material.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Question 3 -->
            <div class="faq-item bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300">
                <button class="faq-question w-full flex justify-between items-center text-left p-5 hover:bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
                    <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#0B2A4F]">How does the AI Revision Tool create mnemonics?</span>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down transition-transform duration-300"></i>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer hidden p-5 border-t border-gray-200">
                    <p class="text-[#6C757D]">When you provide a list of terms, our AI uses its creative capabilities to generate a memorable sentence or story that connects them. We've specifically instructed it to use relatable Indian cultural references (like movies, cricket, or food) to make the mnemonics even more effective and easier to recall during exams.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Question 4 -->
            <div class="faq-item bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300">
                <button class="faq-question w-full flex justify-between items-center text-left p-5 hover:bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
                    <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#0B2A4F]">What kind of feedback do I get after taking a Mock Test?</span>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down transition-transform duration-300"></i>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer hidden p-5 border-t border-gray-200">
                    <p class="text-[#6C757D]">After completing a test, you don't just get a score. The AI provides a detailed performance analysis, including a breakdown of your incorrect answers with clear explanations for the correct concepts. It also identifies your weak areas and suggests key sub-topics you should revise, giving you a personalized roadmap for improvement.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
